{"title":"相关命令","slug":"相关命令","date":"2020-03-28T08:59:38.000Z","updated":"2020-03-28T09:14:15.056Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/相关命令.json","photos":[],"link":"","excerpt":"#相关命令<br>相关的常用hexo命令集<br>","covers":["/2020/03/28/相关命令/1.png"],"content":"<p>#相关命令<br>相关的常用hexo命令集<br><a id=\"more\"></a><br><img src=\"/2020/03/28/相关命令/1.png\" alt=\"Git\"></p>\n<p>##相关命令：<br>这篇文章主要是开启博客的书写历程，并记录一下相关博文的命令行<br>在hexo所在目录下，打开terminal，在命令行输入：<br><figure class=\"highlight plain\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">hexo new a</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo new draft b#草稿文件</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo server --draft#预览草稿文件</span><br><span class=\"line\">hexo publish b#发布草稿文件</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>\n<p>相关发布命令</p>\n<pre><code>hexo g#生成静态文件\nhexo s -p 5000#启动服务器在5000端口，默认4000\nhexo d#hexo deploy 发布到github\n\n</code></pre><p>a是文章标题，也可以加上双引号,如“a”。</p>\n","categories":[],"tags":[]}